# .degitignore

<!-- Excludes the .github folder (issue/PR templates, workflows) when using degit -->

.github

<!-- Excludes the SECURITY.md file (security policy, not needed in a one-off project) -->

SECURITY.md

<!-- Excludes the CHANGELOG (changelog is template-related, not needed in one-off projects) -->

CHANGELOG.md

<!-- Excludes the Code of Conduct (community guidelines only for template repo) -->

CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md

<!-- Excludes contributing guidelines (not relevant in duplicated single projects) -->

CONTRIBUTING.md

<!-- Excludes support docs (only needed for template repo management) -->

SUPPORT.md
